<h1>What is Fulfillment? Everything an Online Seller Needs to Know</h1>

<AuthorByline lang="en" datePublished="2026-04-03" readingTime="12" />

<p class="blog-lead">Global e-commerce crossed $6.3 trillion in 2024 and shows no signs of slowing down. Yet the single biggest bottleneck for growing online stores is not marketing or product development &mdash; it is logistics. Packing boxes, printing labels, queuing at the post office, handling returns. Fulfillment exists to remove that bottleneck entirely, so you can focus on what actually grows your business.</p>

